<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="amz" href="https://www.amazon.com/RC-Pet-Products-Adventure-53803335/dp/B07ZQY48X8/?tag=wwwallabou001-20" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">View on Amazon</a></p>
<p>If you plan to take your cat on outdoor adventures, you need a durable cat harness that offers a snug and comfortable fit – one that won’t restrict your cat’s movements. This RC Pets Adventure Kitty cat harness is fully adjustable at the neck and waist to keep your cat comfortable, and it is made with breathable mesh fabric.</p>
<p>This cat harness comes in two different versions, one of which (the Primary Collection) must be slipped over your cat’s head to put it on. If your cat doesn’t like this kind of harness, the version we’ve chosen might be a better fit. It has buckles at the neck and waist for convenience.</p>
<p>Priced around $27, this harness may be a little more expensive than some options, but it comes in several colors and patterns, and it comes with an included 6-foot leash.</p>
<h3>Pros</h3>
<ul class="pro">
<li>Fully adjustable neck and waist</li>
<li>Air-mesh fabric for breathability and comfort</li>
<li>Durable materials are machine washable</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cons</h3>
<ul class="con">
<li>One design requires harness to be slipped over the head</li>
<li>May not be as secure as other designs</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="su-row card-review">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span class="product-review-heading">#6 </span>Best For Small Cats: Puppia RiteFit Soft Dog Harness</h2>
<p><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-55073 aligncenter" src="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Puppia-RiteFit-Soft-Dog-Harness.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="400" srcset="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Puppia-RiteFit-Soft-Dog-Harness.jpg 400w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Puppia-RiteFit-Soft-Dog-Harness-180x180.jpg 180w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Puppia-RiteFit-Soft-Dog-Harness-60x60.jpg 60w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Puppia-RiteFit-Soft-Dog-Harness-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="amz" href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:best-cat-harness/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fpuppia-ritefit-polyester-back-clip%2Fdp%2F132210" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">View on Chewy</a> <a class="amz" href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00KCLFTRQ/?tag=wwwallabou001-20" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">View on Amazon</a></p>
<p>Remember how we said harnesses made for dogs aren’t usually a great fit for cats? This harness is an exception to that rule. It offers several features that make it work well as a harness for cats.</p>
<p>The Puppia RiteFit harness is a step-in harness, which means that you don’t need to slip it over your cat’s head. The neck is adjustable with both a hook and loop closure and two quick release buckles, allowing you to get a secure, comfortable fit.</p>
<p>The harness is constructed from soft, breathable mesh material that makes it comfy for all activities, including outdoor exploration. On Amazon, the customer review section is filled with photos of cats adventuring outside while wearing their Puppia harness.</p>
<p>In addition to being comfortable and secure, the Puppia harness comes in seven different sizes, so you can easily find one that fits even a small cat. It is affordably priced under $15 as well, and it comes in over a dozen different colors.</p>
<h3>Pros</h3>
<ul class="pro">
<li>Step-in design that doesn’t slip over your cat’s head</li>
<li>Highly adjustable for a safe, secure fit</li>
<li>Wide straps distribute weight evenly across your cat’s chest</li>
<li>Secure enough for outdoor adventures</li>
<li>Available in a variety of colors</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cons</h3>
<ul class="con">
<li>Designed for small dogs, may be too short for some cats</li>
<li>Bulky around the neck</li>
<li>The hook and loop closure may frighten some cats</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="su-row card-review">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span class="product-review-heading">#7 </span>Best For Large Cats: Best Pet Supplies Voyager Step-In Pet Harness</h2>
<p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-50351 aligncenter" src="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Best-Pet-Supplies-Voyager-Step-In-Pet-Harness.jpg" alt="" width="380" height="380" srcset="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Best-Pet-Supplies-Voyager-Step-In-Pet-Harness.jpg 380w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Best-Pet-Supplies-Voyager-Step-In-Pet-Harness-180x180.jpg 180w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Best-Pet-Supplies-Voyager-Step-In-Pet-Harness-60x60.jpg 60w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Best-Pet-Supplies-Voyager-Step-In-Pet-Harness-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="amz" href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:best-cat-harness/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Fbest-pet-supplies-voyager-black-trim%2Fdp%2F134475" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">View on Chewy</a> <a class="amz" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00M0V7WO4/?tag=wwwallabou001-20" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">View on Amazon</a></p>
<p>The Voyager harness from Best Pet Supplies comes in a wide variety of colors and many different sizes. It has a step-in design that allows you to easily insert your cat’s paws through the leg holes and then fasten the harness on their back.</p>
<p>Because this design allows you to put on the harness without ever slipping anything over your cat’s head, it’s comfortable and easy to put on.</p>
<p>The arm holes in this harness are nice and roomy, but the harness isn’t adjustable. That means that the fit isn’t particularly secure. Because it’s not the safest harness for high-risk situations, it’s a good idea to avoid this product if you’re going into remote or noisy areas where your cat might try to escape the harness.</p>
<p>That being said, the Voyager harness is ideal for short, casual trips or exceptionally calm cats with a lot of harness-wearing experience. Because it comes in so many different sizes, it is also a great option for larger cats that don’t fit into traditional cat harnesses.</p>
<h3>Pros</h3>
<ul class="pro">
<li>Extremely comfortable with wide straps</li>
<li>All-season design made from soft, breathable mesh material</li>
<li>Perfect for cats who don’t like having garments slipped over their heads</li>
<li>Available in a variety of colors</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cons</h3>
<ul class="con">
<li>Limited adjustability and large arm holes make this harness less secure than some others</li>
<li>Features a hook-and-loop closure, which might disturb some cats</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="su-row card-review">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span class="product-review-heading">#8 </span>Best For Kittens: Frisco Wrap Cat Harness</h2>
<p><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-31649 aligncenter" src="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Frisco-Wrap-Cat-Harness.jpg" alt="" width="345" height="350" srcset="https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Frisco-Wrap-Cat-Harness.jpg 345w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Frisco-Wrap-Cat-Harness-60x60.jpg 60w, https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Frisco-Wrap-Cat-Harness-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="amz" href="https://prf.hn/click/camref:1101l4atA/pubref:best-cat-harness/destination:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chewy.com%2Ffrisco-wrap-cat-harness%2Fdp%2F257198" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener noreferrer">View on Chewy</a></p>
<p>Many of the pet harnesses on the market are designed with dogs in mind. The Frisco Wrap Cat Harness is not only designed specifically for cats, but it is particularly good for small cats and kittens.</p>
<p>The Frisco Cat Wrap Harness features adjustable straps at the chest and belly that can be adjusted to a girth as small as 9 inches. The hook and loop closures make it easy to ensure a snug fit, no matter your cat’s size, and there is a D-ring on the back to attach the included leash.</p>
<p>Perfect for use as a walking vest or for quick car trips, this cat harness is made from breathable poly/cotton materials for maximum comfort. The materials are also easy to clean, though they are not machine washable. Simply hand wash and hang dry.</p>
<p>Though this harness is an excellent option for kittens, it only comes in two sizes (small and medium), so it may not be ideal for larger cats. It is also a little more expensive than some of the harnesses on this list, priced around $25.</p>
<h3>Pros</h3>
<ul class="pro">
<li>Ideal for smaller cats up to 16inches in girth</li>
<li>Vest-style design with hook and loop closures</li>
<li>Wide, adjustable neck and belly straps</li>
<li>Made from breathable poly/cotton materials</li>
<li>Comes with a matching leash for taking walks</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cons</h3>
<ul class="con">
<li>May be too small for larger cats</li>
<li>Slightly more expensive than some harnesses</li>
<li>Some cats may not like hook and loop closures</li>
</ul>
</div>
<p><strong>Your cat harness is a travel essential, and so is a great cat carrier. </strong><a href="https://allaboutcats.com/best-cat-carrier" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Click here for a guide to the best cat carriers of 2022.</strong></a></p>
